    "title": "Hiring Logistics Manager at Snapdeal Logistics Holdings Services",
    "description": "Join the Snapdeal Logistics Holdings Services family as a Logistics Manager in Meerut. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Snapdeal Logistics Holdings Services:\nSnapdeal Logistics Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Snapdeal Logistics Holdings Services!",
